            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>交易台(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TTD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TTD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TTD-US</a>)截至台北時間27日23:07股價下跌1.7美元，報32.12美元，跌幅5.01%，成交量3,535,426（股），盤中最高價33.57美元、最低價32.12美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.93%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.37%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.75%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+2.16%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>交易台(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TTD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TTD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TTD-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+7.03%</li> <li>近 1 月：-4.59%</li> <li>近 3 月：-31.82%</li> <li>近 6 月：-57.57%</li> <li>今年以來：-3%</li></ul></section></main>",
